83
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,321
Are you feeling better?

84
00:06:44,881 --> 00:06:45,841
Thank you, Miss Zhuo.

85
00:06:46,001 --> 00:06:47,041
I am much better.

86
00:06:49,601 --> 00:06:50,601
Where is my master?

87
00:06:50,721 --> 00:06:52,321
He transmits spiritual power
to you every day,

88
