92
00:07:00,881 --> 00:07:02,721
Heart Poison is spreading in this town

93
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,200
and there's not a minute to lose.

94
00:07:04,761 --> 00:07:05,881
I can help.

95
00:07:06,561 --> 00:07:07,281
No need.

96
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,240
