202
00:12:05,841 --> 00:12:06,560
Immortal lady.

203
00:12:06,921 --> 00:12:09,161
Kill me.

204
00:12:09,481 --> 00:12:11,681
- Immortal lady, it's our fault.
- Don't worry.

205
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,481
These things didn't actually happen,

206
